data.description: Welcome to this stunning Craftsman luxury home, meticulously remodeled to perfection! Step inside and immerse yourself in the epitome of modern elegance and comfort. Main Level:As you enter, be greeted by soaring high ceilings that amplify the sense of space and luxury.  Engineered hardwood floors grace the entirety of the first floor and staircase, offering both durability and aesthetic appeal.  Illuminate your living space with the ambiance of new lighting fixtures thoughtfully placed throughout.  The expansive living room seamlessly flows into the chef's kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining and daily living.  Indulge your culinary passions in the chef's kitchen, featuring Quartz countertops, an apron sink, stainless steel appliances including double ovens and a gas cooktop, a large pantry for ample storage, and a recessed microwave. A newly updated half bathroom with contemporary tile adds convenience, style, and a touch of refinement to the main level. Fresh interior paint revitalizes the space of the entire home.  Upstairs:Retreat to the oversized primary bedroom, complete with a cozy sitting room and his-and-her closets, providing a sanctuary of relaxation and luxury.  Soft new luxe carpeting blankets the top floor, offering plush comfort underfoot.   Jack and Jill bedrooms provide convenience and privacy, perfect for families or guests.  Additionally, a separate secondary bedroom boasts its own en suite bath, ensuring comfort and convenience for all.  Basement:Descend to the fully renovated basement, where new LVP flooring sets the stage for versatile living spaces.  Enjoy quality time with loved ones in the spacious family area or entertain guests at the sleek bar nook.  A generously sized bedroom, currently utilized as a movie room, offers endless possibilities for use and enjoyment.  Outside:Step out onto the deck, where you can unwind and take in serene views of the flat fenced-in backyard, providing a perfect setting for outdoor relaxation and recreation.  Exterior:The three-car garage, complete with a side friendship door, offers ample parking and storage space.  Fresh exterior paint enhances the curb appeal of this exquisite home, inviting you to experience luxury from every angle.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this impeccably remodeled Craftsman luxury home your own. Schedule a viewing today and prepare to indulge in a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication!
